Interface PostAdapter.OnPostClickListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DiscussionPostsActivity
    Enclosing class:
    PostAdapter

    public static interface PostAdapter.OnPostClickListener
    This interface handles callbacks for two cases:

    • The comment reply string being pressed.
    • The comment text being pressed.
